[
  {
    "id": "20240904-01",
    "segments": [
      {
        "start_time": "0:01",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "This way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:07",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:08",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:11",
        "end_time": "0:12",
        "text": "原來是"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:13",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮事"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "ICRNT's News for Kids"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:20",
        "end_time": "0:25",
        "text": "In Taiwan, many kids from 11 to 13 years old"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:25",
        "end_time": "0:27",
        "text": "took a survey."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:27",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "70% said they needed more exercise."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:33",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:33",
        "end_time": "0:34",
        "text": "You know what?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:34",
        "end_time": "0:35",
        "text": "They're right."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:35",
        "end_time": "0:41",
        "text": "台灣很多11歲到13歲的小朋友填問卷調查"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:41",
        "end_time": "0:45",
        "text": "有70%的說他們需要運動"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:45",
        "end_time": "0:47",
        "text": "他們說的沒錯"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:47",
        "end_time": "0:53",
        "text": "Kids from 5 to 17 years old need 1 hour of exercise a day"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:53",
        "end_time": "0:57",
        "text": "That's 7 hours of exercise a week"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:57",
        "end_time": "1:02",
        "text": "5到17歲的孩童需要每天運動1小時"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:02",
        "end_time": "1:04",
        "text": "一週要7個小時"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:12",
        "end_time": "1:21",
        "text": "雖然學校有體育課,但大多數一週只上八十到九十分鐘"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:21",
        "end_time": "1:37",
        "text": "運動可以讓兒童更健康"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:37",
        "end_time": "1:39",
        "text": "我們可以多動動"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:39",
        "end_time": "1:44",
        "text": "像是走樓梯、遛狗或騎腳踏車"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:44",
        "end_time": "1:47",
        "text": "現在外面太熱了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:47",
        "end_time": "1:49",
        "text": "夏天的溫度很猛"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:49",
        "end_time": "1:52",
        "text": "但有很多方法可以讓兒童更健康"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:53",
        "end_time": "2:01",
        "text": "我們可以跳舞、游泳、跳鋼管、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:03",
        "end_time": "2:04",
        "text": "玩耳環球、"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:05",
        "end_time": "2:08",
        "text": "玩耳環球、"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:09",
        "end_time": "2:15",
        "text": "玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、玩耳環球、"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:16",
        "end_time": "2:21",
        "text": "玩耳環球、玩耳�"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:21",
        "end_time": "2:26",
        "text": "And we don't want to make people angry when we exercise at home."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:27",
        "end_time": "2:35",
        "text": "我们需要安全的空间做运动,我们也不想在家做运动的时候,惹怒其他人。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:35",
        "end_time": "2:37",
        "text": "Do you exercise one hour a day?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:38",
        "end_time": "2:38",
        "text": "No?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:38",
        "end_time": "2:39",
        "text": "Why are you sitting?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:40",
        "end_time": "2:43",
        "text": "If your teacher says okay, go and move."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:44",
        "end_time": "2:45",
        "text": "Vocabulary"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:45",
        "end_time": "2:50",
        "text": "一个星期两三堂的体育课,对儿童和青少年是不够的。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:50",
        "end_time": "2:56",
        "text": "Wendy, let's go rollerblading at the park this afternoon."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:57",
        "end_time": "3:00",
        "text": "Wendy, 我们今天下午去公园溜直排轮吧。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:01",
        "end_time": "3:02",
        "text": "No, it's too hot."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:03",
        "end_time": "3:04",
        "text": "不要,太热了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:04",
        "end_time": "3:07",
        "text": "Please, you need exercise."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:07",
        "end_time": "3:09",
        "text": "拜托啦,你需要运动。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:10",
        "end_time": "3:11",
        "text": "Healthier, 更健康。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:12",
        "end_time": "3:14",
        "text": "No, I need to study."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:14",
        "end_time": "3:16",
        "text": "不了,我要读书。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:16",
        "end_time": "3:21",
        "text": "Rollerblading will make you healthier, 直排輪會讓你更健康。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:21",
        "end_time": "3:27",
        "text": "I'm already very healthy thanks to you, 我已經很健康了,都是你的功勞。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:27",
        "end_time": "3:28",
        "text": "Hour, 鐘頭。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:29",
        "end_time": "3:33",
        "text": "Still, experts say you need to work out for one hour every day."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:34",
        "end_time": "3:37",
        "text": "還是一樣,專家說你需要每天動一個鐘頭。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:38",
        "end_time": "3:39",
        "text": "Leave me alone, mom."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:40",
        "end_time": "3:41",
        "text": "媽媽,不要再吵我了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:41",
        "end_time": "3:43",
        "text": "SWIM 游泳"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:43",
        "end_time": "3:47",
        "text": "Alright, I'll go swimming all by myself"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:47",
        "end_time": "3:49",
        "text": "好吧,我就自己去游泳吧"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:50",
        "end_time": "3:53",
        "text": "What kind of exercise do you like?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:53",
        "end_time": "3:54",
        "text": "Exercise"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:56",
        "end_time": "3:57",
        "text": "运动"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:57",
        "end_time": "3:58",
        "text": "Healthier"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:59",
        "end_time": "4:00",
        "text": "更健康"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:00",
